column5: Hello guys,  At the beginning of this winter i tried to organize an ice fishing weekend for a big group at Nosbonsing lake. Booked cottages and ice huts and now i end up with 5 guys cancelling...right now we are only 7 and there's room for at least 5 more...if anybody is interested to come pm me and i will tell you the details...how much $, where and any other info you want. Looks like the forum is my last resort...or not?  Cheers!  Gino
still room for more...good price, too...pm me for details
If I wasn't already commited this weekend, I'd swing by for a visit.
